{"tid":468108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅十字會各類血型血液存量降至極短缺水平　籲市民捐血(14/11/2017)","createTime":"2017-11-14T05:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T11:40:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d180aff003bee1001f5d3c917c4aa03c3a585fe5","tid":468108,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"香港紅十字會輸血服務中心緊急呼籲合資格市民前往捐血。<br />\n<br />\n中心發言人說，目前各類血型的血液存量均已經降至極短缺水平，在未來一星期，中心需要即時得到更多市民捐血作補充，才能夠繼續維持正常血液供應，為病人提供適切臨床輸血治療。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，雖然中心在上月底作出呼籲並加強宣傳，但捐血人數在過去數星期一直未能達到每天1千1百人的目標，血液供求正面對極大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n為方便市民捐血，本月17至19日於沙田和觀塘捐血站的服務時間，將會延長至晚上8時。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1364699-20171114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1364699-20171114.htm&d=UPjA6PuRRITyKL%2B8B9ZvRPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=2ee5a3c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1364699-20171114.htm&h=5917bd35\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1364699-20171114.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2cea813260bc974d0930d9e48afaf628b2e78204","tid":468108,"uid":2267,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"好想捐，但鐵質唔夠，所以不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cc7b8cdf79f1535b1ff52f240cdf985cb03457","tid":468108,"uid":22858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"血壓低，不了"},{"pid":"8383293c05ccd18bca6034c30925feca74f155eb","tid":468108,"uid":38671,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"又短缺"},{"pid":"88f091f2cf038062471dc3fb3c0b9f1d22e6d17d","tid":468108,"uid":498,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"紅十字會公佈左各公私院血液使用分配同埋本地及境外蝗使用比例未<br />\n一日未公佈..一日都不了"},{"pid":"504cad319ccfd662964b2d4cd412af6960d92af6","ti